{
  "texts": [
    "Each group used a different version of RELEX.",
    "Figure 3 shows the interface for the four treatment groups experiencing varying levels of adaptive feedback and reflection guidance.",
    "The grid has two axes: Reflective Prompts and Adaptive Feedback.",
    "Each axis has two options: With and without.",
    "Thus, each quadrant represents a distinct group differentiated by the presence or absence of adaptive feedback and reflection prompts."
  ]
}